<html>
  <head>
    <title>XDSSPARK</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body
    style="width:800px; margin:50px auto;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"
  >
    <table
      style="border:1px solid #dddddd;width:100%;border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr><td
         style="text-align:center;background-image: url('{{websiteMailBgUrl}}'); background-size: cover;background-position: center;padding:10px"
        >
        <img src="{{websiteLogoUrl}}" alt="XDS-SPARK" width="150" />
        </td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:0 20px">
          <p style="padding-top:10px">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
          <p>You are receiving the email because you have two factor authentication (2FA) enabled in your XDS Spark settings, and you have attempted to log in.</p>
          <p>Your one-time security code is:</p>
          <p><b>{{otpString}}</b></p>
          <p>If you would like to remove 2FA, log into Spark and go to Personal Settings and Security Settings.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:20px">Thanks,</p>
          <p>Your friends at XDS Spark</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>